\[fn:2] Def 2
"
    (org-test-with-temp-text "
Text[fn:1][fn:2]

\[fn:2] Def 2

\[fn:1] Def 1"
      (let ((org-footnote-section nil)) (org-footnote-sort))
      (buffer-string))))
  (should
   (equal
    "
* H1
